{"tid":1491582,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"(攬炒情景題）國內朋友遊行完俾海關扣左，救唔救？","createTime":"2019-08-20T13:08:27.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-20T13:34:55.000Z","uid":235074,"like":9,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"1137045fb64eb40a2685c9c27bc2a7c8aeea8636","tid":1491582,"uid":235074,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T13:08:27.000Z","msg":"是咁的，今日返工聽到個狀況<br />\n<br />\n國內同事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n國內同事朋友<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />去完香港某日遊行，返大陸海關唔記得刪相俾人扣留左，<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />打俾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />求救保釋，各位點睇？<br />\n<br />\n正評<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />:唔割，朋友有今生冇來世，信用評分一齊扣1000去救佢，海關以後會當你同黨<br />\n<br />\n負評<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：割，扣信用評分影響冇得借＄/去旅行，叫佢搵其他人擔保佢保釋"},{"pid":"7f1a50347347ea0fda5137c6242b53bae06c4fdc","tid":1491582,"uid":143987,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T13:11:23.000Z","msg":"唔割<br />\n唔係下次到你出事<br />\n邊個會救"},{"pid":"99d9f8d8bdd55d5205ef6d51c53af0a1c6bbde03","tid":1491582,"uid":14135,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T13:30:22.000Z","msg":"唔割"},{"pid":"b5b12dd55d78c679af15de64fed2e5472a5231f0","tid":1491582,"uid":276150,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T13:34:55.000Z","msg":"唔割"}]}